milestones.description: This is the highest match aggregate (424) involving teams New Zealand & Pakistan in ODIs
Wasim Bari has broken the record for most dismissals in an innings (4) in ODIs for PAK, going past Wasim Bari's 3
Abdul Qadir and Rashid Khan's 28-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 24 between Liaqat Ali and Sikander Bakht
